    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. I'm really sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
