    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously preserved since day one. This vehicle features a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. The interior remains in 'time-capsule' condition\u2014the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with every record organized in a comprehensive binder. It has been strictly garage-kept, never driven in inclement weather, and features a completely clean undercarriage free of any oxidation. From the unmarked alloy wheels wrapped in fresh high-performance rubber to the crystal-clear headlight lenses, every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards for a discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new vehicle that has been maintained with an open checkbook.",
      "price": 46500.0,
